  <pre><code>https://api.valter.sens.legal/api/v1</code></pre>

  <h2>What you will find in the canonical docs</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>50+ routes for search, verification, reasoning, chat, and workflows</li>
    <li>OAuth 2.0 Authorization Code Flow with PKCE and tiered access (Free / Pro)</li>
    <li>Updated integration examples and payloads</li>
    <li>Cross-links to Valter's MCP and architecture docs</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Canonical documentation</h2>

